pageContext.claim: “Well, it's a false narrative, and it's shocking, except that they're corrupt. The media is a part of the Democrat Party, essentially, and the media is very corrupt.”
pageContext.analysis: Trump falsely attacks the news media as "corrupt" and "part of the Democratic Party" for accurately reporting details of his interactions with the Ukrainian government. Trump frequently says unflattering news is "fake" but here he ups the ante even more.
